*
 * @module QueryHelper.create
 *
 * 
 * @version 1.0
 * @param Required {Object} {
 *     langCode{String} = 'zh-TW',   
 *     modelName{String} = null,      Sequelize Model 
 *     include{Object|Array} = null,  Sequelize include Query
 *     input{Object} = null,         
 *   }
 * @param Optional {Object} {
 *     format{Object} = null,        
 *     formatCb{Object} = null,       callback
 *   }
 * @example  input  User  Parent  Passport formatCb
 * QueryHelper.create({
 *    modelName: 'User',
 *    include: [Parent, Passport],
 *    input: rawData,
 *  }, {
 *    format,
 *    formatCb: e => ({
 *      ...e,
 *     username: rawData.Parent.idNumber,
 *    }),
 * });
 * @returns {Object} created item
